The paper focuses on the design and implementation of a distributed database system, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the requirements and design of the system, which is related to Database Systems (cs.DB) and Software Engineering (cs.SE). The system's ability to adapt to dynamically changing sets of machines and ensure availability relates to Distributed Systems (cs.DS) and System and Control (cs.SY).
